Author: YiZhiKan,
Description: Yi Feng, a pharmaceutical botanist graduate from Tangdu University dedicates himself to make his fellow villagers rich from cultivating red sage. The circumstances left him dumbstruck. Burdened by the pressure from the mafia and the villagers, our farmer with a green thumb obtained a mysterious power and that became an important turning point of his life. With that, his relationship with his neighbor's daughter, ex-girlfriend (also first love), and the daughter of the pharmacy started to develop. What will his choice be?
